            <div type="translation" xml:lang="en" resp="#edd"><p>Loukios Aboukios <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign xml:lang="la">Lucius Abuccius</foreign></supplied> Eutychos.</p></div></div>
         
         <div type="commentary">
            <head>Commentary</head>
            <p>A superscript bar above the first letter shows that it is a praenomen.</p>
            <p> For the last two letters of the nomen Ἀβούκιος/Abuccius (for which see W.Schulze, 
               <title><ref target="https://zenon.dainst.org/Record/000205459">Zur Geschichte Lateinischer Eigennamen</ref></title>, p. 359) 
               the cutter dropped register in order to avoid a crack in the stone.</p>
